OL,3,CDad with terminal cancer wins Pride of
OL,4,CBritain award for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FCraig Maxwell, who has raised more
OL,7,Fthan a million pounds for a project
OL,8,Fwhich aims to shorten the time it
OL,9,Ftakes to diagnose lung cancer in
OL,10,Fpatients in Wales, is this year's
OL,11,FPride of Britain Regional Fundraiser
OL,12,Fof the Year in Wales.
OL,14,FCraig was one of four finalists whose
OL,15,Finspiring stories have been
OL,16,Fhighlighted by ITV Cymru Wales this
OL,17,Fweek.
OL,19,FHe now goes on to ITV's Pride of
OL,20,FBritain UK awards in London next month.
