OL,3,CDad with terminal cancer wins Pride of
OL,4,CBritain award for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FCraig was diagnosed with non-smoking
OL,7,Fstage-four lung cancer, which is
OL,8,Fcaused by changes to a gene in the
OL,9,Fbody.
OL,11,FIt took 78 days to be diagnosed, a
OL,12,Fsituation he set out to change by
OL,13,Fraising funds for the QuicDNA project
OL,14,Fwhich hopes to cut that wait down to
OL,15,F26 days.
OL,17,FOn receiving the award, presented by
OL,18,FITV Wales' Andrea Byrne at his Penarth
OL,19,Fhome, he said: "To be amongst those
OL,20,Famazing people shortlisted is just
OL,21,Famazing and this is a real surprise.
