OL,3,CDad with terminal cancer wins Pride of
OL,4,CBritain award for fundraising efforts
OL,6,F"I just want to say a big thank you to
OL,7,Feveryone who has supported me in all
OL,8,Fthe fundraising activities.
OL,10,F"It just goes to show how much this
OL,11,Fdisease affects so many people.
OL,13,F"I had surgery last week to remove two
OL,14,Fsmall parts of my lung and I have been
OL,15,Fhaving recovery time. We've booked as
OL,16,Fa family to go to Disneyland at the
OL,17,Fend of October and then I will be
OL,18,Fcycling 500 miles across Florida with
OL,19,FVelindre to raise more funds."
