OL,3,CDad with terminal cancer wins Pride of
OL,4,CBritain award for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FHis mum Sue said: "We are so proud of
OL,7,Fhim. He is unbelievable. I don't know
OL,8,Fwhere he gets the strength from. He
OL,9,Fjust keeps going."
OL,11,FHis wife Tracey said: "We are really
OL,12,Fproud of him. We are here to support
OL,13,Fhim."
